{"tid":2057462,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔搭黨鐵 唔食美心 唔係好難","createTime":"2020-06-09T11:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T12:20:14.000Z","uid":100596,"like":37,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7a8a8d4df09045a392b1a1f637d94a098019b5d1","tid":2057462,"uid":100596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"一年前既我，每日迫黨鐵，返工一出閘就幫襯美心買早餐，就算勁多人排都無得揀。放工就陪呀媽睇tvb 膠劇，佢膠時我又膠。<br />\n<br />\n一年後，而家搭過海巴士返工放工，日日有位坐，無諗過車程可以快過黨鐵，仲可以一程到尾，不知幾舒服。落車經過舊式餅鋪就入去買早餐。<br />\n<br />\n每日食完飯就入房煲下美劇。愛回家，降魔的個d 真係唔知仲有咩人會睇。如果想開電視，就轉去ViuTV ，發覺都幾好睇，星期六日晚仲有好多好戲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n習慣，只要肯改，每日行出一少步，就做到。"},{"pid":"55f4865f8b26c3bdfcaa7b81f9032238f4e8c9f4","tid":2057462,"uid":19055,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"屯公日日都塞車，點搭巴士呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795de23d140deb4183fde3e86e503588a8b9379a","tid":2057462,"uid":229397,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"唔食美心有關食肆真係好簡單。唔搭黨鐵真係有難度, 好似樓上咁, 住某啲地方, 喺某啲地方返工真係冇辦法冇得揀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1712ada3182e91f5d9da3d983721fbee69663e5","tid":2057462,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"55f4865f8b26c3bdfcaa7b81f9032238f4e8c9f4","tid":2057462,"uid":19055,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"屯公日日都塞車，點搭巴士呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"日日早起身兩個鐘<br />\n咁都做唔到?"},{"pid":"3c3c44034af57572319d663fd607b7b5a50fdff2","tid":2057462,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:12:58.000Z","msg":"到家下都仲睇cctvb 食藍店 <br />\n我只可以講你地根本無恆心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46323429ddd051a0077fd493f6bcc5674af4d91b","tid":2057462,"uid":207639,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:15:31.000Z","msg":"如果黨鐵快過巴士你咪又係搭返黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af57cd3270988ae1110a012776fe5bacfca6880","tid":2057462,"uid":226850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:16:07.000Z","msg":"大把所謂淺黃仲覺得食藍店係無所謂好小事<br />\n睇嚟革命真係只是請客食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4ccaf654df3d2e20e138d87e933190a4bf86b1","tid":2057462,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:17:03.000Z","msg":"你個標題漏左「對我來講」4隻字"},{"pid":"0bd1b3743766411ca891f7400651fc3fbcc51501","tid":2057462,"uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1712ada3182e91f5d9da3d983721fbee69663e5","tid":2057462,"uid":294121,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"55f4865f8b26c3bdfcaa7b81f9032238f4e8c9f4","tid":2057462,"uid":19055,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:31:30.000Z","msg":"屯公日日都塞車，點搭巴士呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"日日早起身兩個鐘<br />\n咁都做唔到?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:18:06.000Z","msg":"兩個鐘...<br />\n至少兩百蚊係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa92ced7872a29775f2c7c40016a28a9f6a63063","tid":2057462,"uid":175799,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:20:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">盡量</span>唔搭黨鐵 <span style=\"color: red;\">盡量</span>唔食美心<br />\n<br />\n好多地方唔係有公共交通工具揀<br />\n同埋好多地方方圓一二公里無一間黃店"}]}